Global Mobile Phone Holder for Live Broadcast Market Insights
Mobile Phone Holder for Live Broadcast Market size was valued at USD 0.75 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.85 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 15.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Mobile Phone Holder for Live Broadcast Market Overview
The global mobile phone holder for live broadcast market has experienced robust growth over recent years, driven by the increasing demand for mobile streaming and content creation. The market size in 2023 was valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion, with projections to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 12% from 2024 to 2030. The rise in mobile video content consumption, particularly on social media platforms, is one of the major factors driving this growth. Moreover, the continuous advancement in mobile phone technologies, which enhances live broadcasting capabilities, further contributes to the expansion of this market.

With increasing popularity of live broadcasts in sectors like gaming, education, and entertainment, mobile phone holders tailored for such activities are becoming essential tools for content creators. These holders are designed for hands-free, stable, and versatile setups, which enhance user experience while live-streaming. Regions like North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific are the major markets due to their large population of content creators and growing adoption of live-streaming services.

